reviewText: This is the film by Wendelle Stevens with the UFO Contactee William Herrman who was picked up by a UFO from Zeta Reticuli in 1978. Very Good.

An absolutely believable and fasinating encounter and after story. The hypnosis session alone couldn't have been faked. Though the recording seems dated and not in high quality, its nevertheless completely believable. Anyone looking for ideas for a movie this would be it, no question. What happens after the abduction is equally as fasinating. powermetal38@aol.com
